{"tid":209763,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有 傳 吳 若 希 7 月 即 將 進 軍 紅 館 首 開 個 唱","createTime":"2017-04-20T12:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T14:21:16.000Z","uid":61688,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4b99c669a313da423495dbbd447637fa493e40","tid":209763,"uid":61688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"24歲吳若希(Jinny)去年意外有咗，懷孕初期點都唔認，不過多次被人影到肚凸凸，又去咗男友Alex喺澳門嘅豪宅安胎，再講陀B係一件喜事，吳若希之後就大方認陀囡囡Giselle，今日有周刊指，臨盆在即嘅吳若希，7月將頂替「世紀賤男」鄭俊弘開紅館騷。<br />\n<br />\n據報道講吳若希要生B、鍾嘉欣長居加國、許廷鏗想離巢，鄭俊弘絕對係星夢力捧歌手之一，點知近日爆出鄭俊弘背未婚妻暗交何雁詩，形象插水，得罪公司老闆何哲圖，鄭俊弘被掟入雪櫃，何哲圖將紅館7月個檔期俾咗吳若希，而吳若希預產期4月尾，佢就會快速收身，以最佳狀態示人，吳若希一向係「爸B」何哲圖愛將，早前大肚已經講過生完就復出，今次見何哲圖7月個檔唔知搵邊個去頂，佢就好快應承，報道又指，吳若希最近多咗喺社交網貼相係為咗keep人氣囉!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56587965&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56587965%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170420&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3e0bf378\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56587965%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170420&h=b20c668f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56587965&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170420</a>"},{"pid":"c735619377ab34c304e1bce6c547bcfe36c8502d","tid":209763,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:37:28.000Z","msg":"4月底生，7月上紅館，其實有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dfa0c129e29a4ec78533311b269c5a4617f9e7","tid":209763,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4月底生，7月上紅館，其實有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/w